221	// reason so QuotaStatus.Reason carries information only when it adds
222	// value beyond the State enum. The trivial QuotaOK success path
223	// ("fresh snapshot has headroom") is suppressed so the public Status
224	// string matches the contract-003 fixture (bare "ok"). All non-OK
